ewer nook simple touch reader on may   the price was dropped to us in september  the price was dropped again to us in late  nook wifi was discontinued nook simple touch e inkedit main article nook simple touch announced on may   the simple touch reader also informally referred as nook nd edition was released on june   at a retail price of us the simple touch is a wifi only nook with an infrared touchscreen e ink technology and battery life of up to two months or  hours offering approximately  continuous page turns with wifi turned off the device weighs  grams  oz with dimensions of  ×  ×  on november   the simple touch readers price dropped to us on december   the simple touch readers price dropped to us on december   the simple touch readers price dropped to us in february  the simple touch reader was discontinued due to being phased out by the glowlight nook simple touch with glowlight e inkedit main article nook simple touch on april   a nook simple touch reader with builtin led lighting called glowlight was released with a retail price of us on september   the simple touch reader with glowlights price dropped to us on august   the simple touch reader with glowlights price dropped to us on october   the simple touch reader with glowlight was discontinued due to being phased out by the nook glowlight nook color lcdedit main article nook color released on november   and priced at us the nook color comes installed with android  eclair the device is powered by a ti omap   mhz processor and has  mb of ram  gb of flash storage a  lcd screen and a microsd expansion slot on february   the price of the nook color was reduced to us on august   the price of the nook color was reduced to us on november   following the release of the nook hd and nook hd the price of the nook color was reduced to us salesperson demonstrating the nook tablet in a barnes  noble bookstore in livingston new jersey nook tablet lcdedit main article nook tablet the inch nook tablet based on android o