torage became available on november   for us a version with  gb of internal storage was made available february   for us replacing the nook color in that price range on august   the price of the nook tablet  gb and nook tablet  gb were reduced to us and us respectively nook hd and nook hdedit nook hdedit main article nook hd nook hd styled nook hd announced september   and released november   along with the nook hd is a inch tablet with a resolution of x it competes with the inch kindle fire hd and comes in two colors snow and smoke a dark gray it has a texas instruments  ghz dualcore processor with  gb ram it can play back video at p from the nook video store much like amazoncoms instant video service the nook hd was initially priced at us for  gb and us for  gb it then sold at reduced prices at us for  gb and us for  gb the nook hd runs a heavily modified version of android  ice cream sandwich the nook hdhd line was originally planned to be discontinued as announced in barnes and nobles  fiscal yearend report due to financial losses a few months later bn president michael p huseby announced that the company intends to continue to design and develop cuttingedge nook black and white and color devices at the best values in the marketplace following the resignation of former ceo william lynch nook hdedit main article nook hd nook hd styled nook hd is barnes  nobles first tablet capable of playing back movies and television shows downloadable from nook video store at p resolution announced on september   the nook hd is a inch tablet with a  ×  resolution it competes with the similar inch kindle fire hd and has a texas instruments  ghz dualcore omap  processor and was initially priced at us and us for  and  gb respectively then only the  gb model was available at us nook hd runs a heavily modified version of android  samsung galaxy tab  nook  lcdedit on october   bn released the galaxy tab  nook  it features the same specifications as the galaxy tab   so it has a  ghz q